emands a modern multi-core processor, a mid-range GPU, and at least 8GB of RAM for optimal performance.</p>\n<p>Players using older hardware or integrated graphics may encounter crashes or performance bottlenecks. Upgrading components or adjusting in-game settings can alleviate these problems.</p>\n<h3>System Requirements Overview</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Minimum:</strong> Intel Core i5-2300 or AMD FX-4350, 8 GB RAM, NVIDIA GeForce GTX 660 or AMD Radeon HD 7870, DirectX 11.</li>\n<li><strong>Recommended:</strong> Intel Core i7-6700K or AMD Ryzen 5 3600, 16 GB RAM, NVIDIA GeForce GTX 970 or AMD Radeon RX 480, DirectX 11.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Future Outlook and Game Stability Improvements</h2>\n<p>With ongoing support from Awaken Realms, Tainted Grail is expected to evolve with enhanced stability and broader compatibility. Developers have shown commitment to resolving startup crashes through patches and community engagement.</p>\n<p>Players are encouraged to keep their systems updated, report persistent issues with detailed logs, and participate in official forums to expedite troubleshooting processes.</p>\n<p>The challenge of a tainted grail crash on startup, while frustrating, is part of the growing pains for a game that pushes narrative and mechanical boundaries. As fixes accumulate, the community can look forward to a more seamless experience in this atmospheric and strategic RPG world.</p>",
